The Telegraph - Calcutta : Metro

Life

 All for a body beautiful

 The Body Transformation Programme at Talwalkers 

 What: Launch of a Body Transformation Programme at Talwalkers.

 Where: 14A, Burdwan Road, Alipore. 

 When: May 1.

 Take a look: The newly-launched programme aims to help you lose weight through a scientific process. It stresses on the combined effects of proper nutrition and exercise.

 The programme encourages proper diet and calorie expenditure through a professionally planned exercise schedule. It includes Lipase Activity Modification (LAM) oil massages that help reduce fat from different parts of the body.

 Benefits of the programme include mobilisation of fat and inch loss, stimulation of the metabolic system, enhancing blood circulation and improving absorption of nutrients, reduction of muscular stiffness, elimination of toxins from the body and faster muscle repair.

 Pocket pinch: The programme costs Rs 17,000, but there is an inaugural offer till May 9 that allows you to avail of it for Rs 14,000.




